<font color="japanese">（アベル）うわ…

25
00:01:57,952 --> 00:01:59,620
<font color="japanese">（ジキド）ええい やあ！

26
00:01:59,912 --> 00:02:00,746
<font color="japanese">ん？

27
00:02:00,996 --> 00:02:02,164
<font color="japanese">どりゃ〜！

28
