<font color="japanese">あっ！

39
00:02:42,246 --> 00:02:43,789
<font color="japanese">アベル〜！

40
00:02:44,081 --> 00:02:46,709
<font color="japanese">（ガーゴイルたち）グエ〜！

41
00:02:52,006 --> 00:02:52,840
