<font color="japanese">グヘヘヘヘッ…

46
00:03:00,764 --> 00:03:01,599
<font color="japanese">ああ…

47
00:03:01,724 --> 00:03:04,268
<font color="japanese">あっ あ〜 放して！

48
00:03:04,393 --> 00:03:05,728
<font color="japanese">放してよ！

49
00:03:05,853 --> 00:03:06,687
<font color="japanese">うっ！

