80
00:04:56,380 --> 00:04:57,423
<font color="japanese">（ドドンガ）ヘヘッ

81
00:04:58,340 --> 00:04:59,341
<font color="japanese">ウフッ

82
00:05:22,281 --> 00:05:23,615
