<font color="japanese">アベル〜！

115
00:07:09,430 --> 00:07:10,597
<font color="japanese">ティアラ！

116
00:07:11,098 --> 00:07:11,932
<font color="japanese">とりゃ〜！

117
00:07:18,647 --> 00:07:20,107
<font color="japanese">（ジキド）とう！
（アベル）うっ…

118
00:07:20,983 --> 00:07:21,817
<font color="japanese">アベル！

119
00:07:22,234 --> 00:07:23,277
<font color="japanese">来るな！

120
00:07:23,902 --> 00:07:25,237
<font color="japanese">やあ〜！

121
00:07:25,362 --> 00:07:26,363
<font color="japanese">あっ！

122
00:07:30,492 --> 00:07:32,327
