<font color="japanese">アベル〜！　アベル！

125
00:07:48,177 --> 00:07:50,053
<font color="japanese">（ムーア）ムヒョヒョヒョヒョ…

126
00:07:50,179 --> 00:07:51,263
<font color="japanese">（ティアラ）放して！

127
00:07:52,222 --> 00:07:54,057
<font color="japanese">ティアラ…

128
00:08:01,440 --> 00:08:04,151
<font color="japanese">フッフッフッフッ…

129
00:08:05,903 --> 00:08:07,279
<font color="japanese">やめて〜！

130
00:08:07,404 --> 00:08:09,615
<font color="japanese">ムヒョ おとなしくしろ

131
00:08:09,740 --> 00:08:10,574
<font color="japanese">アベル！

132
00:08:13,619 --> 00:08:15,454
<font color="japanese">（ジキド）フッフッフッ…

133
00:08:15,829 --> 00:08:17,289
<font color="japanese">やめて！

134
00:08:17,998 --> 00:08:19,833
<font color="japanese">（ジキド）フッフッフッ…

135
00:08:23,128 --> 00:08:24,254
<font color="japanese">死ね！

136
00:08:24,755 --> 00:08:27,591
<font color="japanese">アベル〜！

137
00:08:30,302 --> 00:08:31,637
<font color="japanese">（ムーア）うわ… はへ！

138
00:08:31,762 --> 00:08:32,596
<font color="japanese">なんだ？

139
00:08:32,971 --> 00:08:33,889
<font color="japanese">あっ…

140
00:08:34,515 --> 00:08:35,599
<font color="japanese">（バラモス）何？

141
00:08:39,311 --> 00:08:41,021
<font color="japanese">いけません ティアラ！

142
00:08:55,786 --> 00:08:57,746
<font color="japanese">（ムーア）ムヒョヒョヒョヒョ

143
