177
00:12:41,887 --> 00:12:43,388
<font color="japanese">（すすり泣き）

178
00:12:48,768 --> 00:12:49,936
<font color="japanese">（咆哮）

179
00:12:52,230 --> 00:12:53,064
<font color="japanese">（ムーア）おいしょ！

180
00:12:53,190 --> 00:12:55,734
<font color="japanese">バラモス様
